item.title: Laurits Fredsgaard Larsen
item.description: About Me I currently study Machine Learning and Data Science at University of Copenhagen. 💻 From my MSc in Molecular Biomedicine, I have lots of practical experience working with protiens, cells and viruses. 👨🏻‍🔬 Research Interest I am interested in all things Machine Learning in Life Science, but I am particularly keen on developing models to support protein research. Publications Fredsgaard L, […]: Head-to-Head Comparison of Modular Vaccines Developed Using Different Capsid Virus-Like Particle Backbones and Antigen Conjugation System.
